lead_paragraph: Jose De Leon was feeling calm shortly before his major league debut until he spotted his brother near the bullpen railing. He reached over and they hugged as De Leon whispered "I did it," leaving Juan near tears.

headline.print_headline: De Leon Notches 9 Ks in MLB Debut; Dodgers Beat Padres 7-4
